#

Classic Tomato Bruschetta

15 min
$8
150 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVegan

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerItalianEasy

Description

A delightful appetizer featuring fresh tomatoes and basil on toasted bread, perfect for any gathering!

Ingredients

  • baguette: 1, sliced
  • tomatoes: 2 cups, diced
  • fresh basil leaves: 1/2 cup, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • balsamic vinegar: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
